message:
@bez the DC1 recovery due to AC units is going to take about 8 hours. If our DC2 encounters an issue we don't have a failover option ready. 
We need to spin up AWS instances and keep them ready just in case. If we try to do that during a disaster it ll take upwards of 2 hours to recitfy. 

However Hamed says it's a costly affair. What're your thoughts?
